Map Name: gg_mr_arena_v3

Version: 3.0

Created By: Paul '[MalReynolds]' Elliott

Email: whde2000@yahoo.co.uk

Dev Notes: gg_mr_arena_v2 is my first map i'm actually proud of and i have many more ideas for similar maps.
Created for the Aerelon Gaming Community http://www.aerelon.com but i want everyone to play it :)

gg_mr_arena is the same map, but without any curving.

Dev textures from FPSBanana http://www.fpsbanana.com/ The person who uploaded did so as a guest. Thanks for the textures.

I never added the textures to the .bsp before so people were getting pink and black squares, so added them now with PakRat.

Spawn Points: 48

[UPDATE] I  found that the author of the textures i used was Chris528, so i've changed this note to reflect it.
